high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the microwave above the stove.
Open the microwave and take the potato out and shut the door of the microwave.
Turn around and then turn to the left to face the fridge.
Put the potato in the fridge and shut the door and then take the potato out and shut the door.
Go left and face the microwave above the stove.
Put the potato in the microwave and shut the door.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the stove, look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave door, take out the potato, close the microwave door.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left.
Open the fridge door, place the potato on the top shelf, close the door, open the door, take the potato out of the fridge, close the door.
Turn left and walk to the stove, look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the potato inside the microwave, close the door.
anns.task_desc: To chill a potato and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the microwave above the stove.
Take the potato out of the microwave.
Turn around with the potato, bring the potato to the fridge on the left.
Chill the potato in the fridge.
Bring the potato back to the microwave on the left.
Put the chilled potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato in the microwave.
